# config-store.js — DRY Config Utility

## Purpose
Centralized read/write for `~/.gemini/agent-portal.json`.
Eliminates path duplication across mcp-proxy, api-routes, etc.

## Exports
- `CONFIG_PATH` — resolved absolute path to config file
- `readConfig()` → `object` — reads + parses, returns `{}` on missing/error
- `writeConfig(obj)` — atomic JSON.stringify + writeFileSync

## Consumers
- `mcp-proxy.js` — loadConfig() reads server list
- `api-routes.js` — install/remove handlers write config
- `web-server.js` — startup config validation
